::GoldenEye::

She saw that all the opposing Preds had left the area. Except for 
one, a mouse who was standing at the front of the ship, yelling.

"What is that little morsal doing? She was with the losing team of 
Preds who were fighting with the ones in the ship. What is she doing, 
changing sides? Well well, there may be some intelegence in that 
little snack.  I mean, why would anyone want to stay with the losing 
team, Hmmmm. I dare say, it is time to make myself known. After all, 
why not go with the winning team?"

She spread her huge, golden wings out and swooped down. She landed in 
a tree near the ship and waited to see what would happen.  She eyed 
the mouse.  She thought, if they don't accept the mouse, she will 
make a nice meal.  She just waited and watched.
